 o if you like\n-You'll find it's a cozy\, relaxed and enjoyable environmen
 t!\n\n***\n\n**Event Fee:** 10 dollars (Cash only at the door) (HST includ
 ed)\nor by e transfer: **steveflemming11@gmail.com**\n\n***\n\n**Friendly 
